docs.snippet: The concentration of military bases, along with business programs for former military personnel, has fueled a growth in entrepreneurship....
docs.lead_paragraph: The concentration of military bases, along with business programs for former military personnel, has fueled a growth in entrepreneurship.
docs.abstract: Military veterans are transforming San Diego, Calif, into hub for entrepreneurs, with many using their connections and expertise to create start-ups that cater to region's high concentration of military bases; circumstances prompt several organizations to help them arrange capital and navigate other complexities.

headline.main: Veterans Help Make San Diego a Hub for Start-Ups
headline.print_headline: San Diego, With the Help of Veterans, Becomes a Hub for Start-Ups
